        {
            "type": 1,
            "content": {
                "json": "## Azure App Service Review\n\n---\n\nThis workbook has been automatically generated out of the checklists in the [Azure Review Checklists repo](https://github.com/Azure/review-checklists). This repo contains best practices and recommendations around generic Landing Zones as well as specific services such as Azure Virtual Desktop, Azure Kubernetes Service or Azure VMware Solution, to name a few. This repository of best practices is curated by Azure engineers, but open to anybody to contribute.\n\nIf you see a problem in the queries that are part of this workbook, please open a Github issue [here](https://github.com/Azure/review-checklists/issues/new)."
            },
            "customWidth": "100",
            "name": "MarkdownHeader"
        },
