                    {
                        "type": 1,
                        "content": {
                            "json": "Use Premium and Standard tiers for staging slots and automated backups. Align your backup retention period with disaster recovery needs. Check [this link](https://learn.microsoft.com/azure/app-service/overview-hosting-plans) for further information."
