                    {
                        "type": 1,
                        "content": {
                            "json": "Implement health checks to monitor and detect issues with App Service instances. Health checks enable automatic instance replacement on failure. Check [this link](https://learn.microsoft.com/azure/app-service/monitor-instances-health-check) for further information."
